struct BinaryAnalysis::InstructionSemantics::MultiSemantics< ValueType0, State0, Policy0, ValueType1, State1, Policy1, ValueType2, State2, Policy2, ValueType3, State3, Policy3 >::SP0

A tag to identify a certain sub-policy or sub-value.

Type type or value of type SPn corresponds to sub-policy n. The numbering is zero-origin. Even if a multi-policy declaration secifies only two sub-policies, all other sub-policy slots are initialized to the NullSemantics policy.
